# Email distribution lists - KX Delta Platform

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/platform/emaildistribution/

# Email distribution lists

To create an email distribution list

  1. Pick the menu item _File > New > Email Distribution List_.

![Screenshot](../img/control/emaildistributionlist1.png)

  2. Name your list.

![Screenshot](../img/control/emaildistributionlist2.png)

  3. Add or remove users from the list and save it.

![Screenshot](../img/control/emaildistributionlist3.png)

